descriptionHtml:
What this mod does:
____________________

This mod adds 17 new moon textures, which include:

Dvorjak
Alopitras
the Moon
Whiright
Hosh
Vulzok
Pae
Yabba
Odwin
Ewonine
Bikuaneul
Illogan
Jasm
Requan
Mexnle III
Tysouv
Falbrune
_________________________________________________________________________________________

AND

Quirky Moons  - This pack includes 10 new moons that won\'t fit the game work, but can make for some fun times nonetheless

Old Man in the Moon
Eye Moon
Cheshire Cat Moon
Sauron Moon
Twisted Moon
Despair Moon
Skull Moon
Undefined Moon
Gizmo Moon
Evil Moon

_________________________________________________________________________________________

Installation:

Extract using winrar

Choose which moon you want, the Masser and/or Secunda version of the moon and then drop the data folder into your Skyrim directory. Overwrite when prompted. It\'s recommended you backup or have the original moon  files ready in case you want to uninstall this. 


_________________________________________________________________________________________

How to Uninstall:

Go to your Skyrim directory \\data\\textures\\sky and delete the masser and secunda files.
author: Lillith
